---
title: KW Ruby Developers
---

%section.hero.text-white.py-md-4
  .container
    .row.py-5
      .col-4.d-none.d-md-block
        .hero-icon
          = svg "ruby"
      .col
        %h1.hero-title.pb-3
          Dedicated to learning and sharing about <a href="http://ruby-lang.org">Ruby</a>
        %p
          All skill levels are welcome.
        %p.pb-1
          We meet once a month for a workshop, training session, or discussion.
        = link_to "Join us!", "https://www.meetup.com/kw-ruby-on-rails/", class: "btn hero-link"

%section.container
  .row.pt-5
    .offset-lg-2

    .col-12.col-md.mb-4
      .float-left{style: 'min-height:100px;'}
        %img.mr-3.ml-4.float-right{src: '/images/meetup.svg', alt: "Meetup", style: "width:60px;"}
      %h5.mt-0 Join us on Meetup
      %p
        See upcoming and past events in the
        = link_to 'meetup page.', 'http://www.meetup.com/kw-ruby-on-rails/'

    .col-12.col-md
      .float-left{style: 'min-height:100px;'}
        %img.mr-0.float-right{src: '/images/reddit.svg', alt: "Reddit", style: "width:100px; margin-top:-20px;"}

      %h5.mt-0 Join us on Reddit
      %p
        Ask questions and chat with locale rubyists using the
        = link_to 'forum', 'https://www.reddit.com/r/kwruby/'
        and
        = link_to 'chat.', 'https://www.reddit.com/chat/r/kwruby/channel/113489992_b94e00a0b7dd4d6232a7624cf3269c90c0fd70e2'

    .offset-lg-2
